DOC.brief_summary: This single-site , 8-visit , double-masked , cross-over study involve three market product study lens . Participants randomly assign lens type , wear approximately two week ( 12 +/- 2 day ) . Participants undergo minimum washout period 3 day enter study undergo minimum 7 day washout period dispense lens type .
